plot: The gang runs into trouble while trying to deliver Serena and Murphy's baby to safety. But is the baby worth saving?

Serena is near to deliver her baby and the group decides to take her to a nearby Mennonite community. When they arrive, 10k, Addy and Doc kill zombies and are sprayed with anthrax. Soon 10k and Addy are sick, but Doc is not affected since he had taken vaccines against many diseases when he served the army. Meanwhile Serena delivers her baby while Warren takes a decision to cure 10k and Addy.—Claudio Carvalho, Rio de Janeiro, Brazil
